## Session Completion

When ending a work session, complete ALL steps:

1. Write session memory to `{{DOCS_MEMORY}}/` via the memory agent
2. Invoke **compact-context** to consolidate memory checkpoints and finalize decided-plans
3. Run quality gates (if code changed)
4. Update work item status via backlog tools
5. Push to remote (MANDATORY)
6. Provide handoff context for next session

